      "content": "i don't even want to \"heal\" anymore. how can you heal something that isn't there? the thing that made me \"me\" is dead. i'm just a collection of habits and obligations. it feels like i'm just taking up space that isn't mine. it would be so much quieter if i could just... stop being this empty version of myself.",
